'''Barrows equipment''' refers to a number of sets of combat [[equipment]] found in the [[Barrows]] [[minigame]]. There are six sets of Barrows equipment: four for [[Combat classes#Warrior|warriors]], one for [[Combat classes#Ranger|rangers]], and one for [[Combat classes#Mage|mages]]. Each set has four pieces: a two-handed weapon (except for [[Ahrim's Staff]], which after an update was changed to be a one-handed weapon like other staffs in an effort to buff the weapon), a helmet, a torso piece, and legwear. When all four pieces for a particular brother are equipped, a [[special set effect]] is granted, which is different for each set. Additionally, the [[amulet of the damned]] enhances the set effects while equipped. Barrows sets cannot be made using the [[Smithing]] [[skill]].

The [[Barrows gloves]], which also resemble a piece of Barrows armour, are not obtained through the Barrows minigame and instead can be purchased after full completion of the [[Recipe for Disaster]] quest.

