==Trivia==
*Upon release, [[Barrows]] equipment did not [[degrade]]; it was changed about a week later in an [[Update:Barrows Changes and Other Tweaks|update]] due to outcry from players claiming it would devalue [[Dragon equipment]].
*Prior to an [[Update:General QoL!|update]], [[guthan's chainskirt]] had transparent sections, similar to [[ghostly robes]].
*[[Dharok's set]] is the only Barrows set that doesn't have an animation after activating its [[set effect]].
*Despite being followers of Saradomin, Barrows equipment does not provide protection from Saradomin's followers in the [[God Wars Dungeon]] (and the [[Wilderness God Wars Dungeon|Wilderness variant]]).

